      • SamSelector

        public SamSelector(SamRevision samRevision,
                   java.lang.String serialNumber,
                   java.lang.String extraInfo)
        Create a SeSelector to perform the SAM selection

        Three optional parameters

        Parameters:
        samRevision - the expected SAM revision (subtype)
        serialNumber - the expected serial number as an hex string (padded with 0 on the left). Can be a sub regex (e.g. "AEC0....") or null to allow any serial number.
        extraInfo - information string (to be printed in logs)

      • SamSelector

        public SamSelector(SamIdentifier samIdentifier,
                   java.lang.String extraInfo)
        Create a SeSelector to perform the SAM selection

        Two optional parameters.

        Parameters:
        samIdentifier - the expected SAM identification: revision (subtype), serial number as an hex string (padded with 0 on the left; can be a sub regex e.g. "AEC0....") and groupReference (not needed here).
        extraInfo - information string (to be printed in logs)
